OL,12,GI am a genealogist who uses maps and
OL,13,Gtechnology to explore how people
OL,14,Glived. Historical GIS (HGIS) applies
OL,15,GGIS tools to historical sources to
OL,16,Gunderstand how places and communities
OL,17,Gchanged over time. In this
OL,18,Gpresentation, I will show how I used
OL,19,GHGIS to aid genealogical research by
OL,20,Gintegrating QGIS with 1840 tithe maps,
